Description:
You find a small grotto with a shrine adorned with spider motifs. It looks unattended, and you wonder why it would be here, as it has nothing to do with the Great Bird. As if reading your mind, Tulah speaks.

(Tulah): “This is strange. I remember being here some days ago. I was about to do something that, at the time, I thought was our only salvation, but a group of adventurers stopped me. It feels strange to be back here.

This was my special place. An old shrine dedicated to some ancient spider spirit that I discovered while working as a priestess in the Great Bird’s temple. This was a place where I could meditate and escape the Great Bird’s influence. I learned a lot here.”
DescriptionAction: Do you want to spend more time here?
